  "style_summary_en": "Michelin 2-star.\n8-seat counter in a converted kimono shop.\n'Bold yet elegant — pure without artifice' aesthetic.\nNo layering of ingredients; creativity emerges from simple presentation.\nDisplays pottery by Rosanjin and other artisans.\nMenu shifts not only with seasonal peaks but also subtle changes (budding greens, moon phases, solar terms).",
  "style_summary_jp": "ミシュラン2つ星。\n元着物店を改装した8席のカウンター。\n「大胆で優雅 — 技巧を排した純粋さ」の美学。\n素材を重ねず、シンプルな外観から創意を発見。\n魯山人など作家作品を小品展示。\n旬のピークだけでなく、微細な変化（新芽、月、節気）に応じた食材の変動。",
  "holistic_signature_en": "Kyoto modern kaiseki standard.\nMinimalist aesthetics and seasonal curation.",
  "holistic_signature_jp": "京都モダン懐石の標準。\nミニマル美学と季節節気のキュレーション。"
